  "Description": {
    "English": "A powerful starship weapon, capable of delivering <span class=\"name name-stellar\">extreme destruction</span> at <span class=\"name name-technology\">close range</span>. <br><br>Note: these particles show <span class=\"name name-title\">decreased effectiveness</span> against shielded targets.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种强大的飞船武器，能够在<span class=\"name name-technology\">近距离范围</span>内提供<span class=\"name name-stellar\">极限破坏力</span>。<br><br>注意：这些炮弹对有护盾的目标<span class=\"name name-title\">有效性降低</span>。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "射击能破坏大片锥形区域内的一切。<br> <br>由于射程和射速有所降低，建议使用者用于近距离目标。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種強大的太空船武器，能在<span class=\"name name-technology\">近距離</span>造成<span class=\"name name-stellar\">極端性破壞</span>。<br><br>注意：對付有防護罩的目標時，這些粒子的<span class=\"name name-title\">效果會降低</span>。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
